# Formations Design System

## Identity
- **Theme:** Formations (Forbes Advisor sub-brand)
- **Font:** Gilroy (sans-serif), Euclid Circular B (secondary)
- **Primary color:** Purple (#4817C2)
- **Secondary color:** Green (#2F7F51)
- **Stack:** Next.js 14+ (App Router), Tailwind CSS, TypeScript
- **Icons:** lucide-react

