### Semantic Usage
- **Primary actions** (buttons, links, focus): primary-500 → primary-600 hover
- **Success/positive**: secondary-500
- **Warnings/highlights**: tertiary-400
- **Errors/destructive**: quaternary-500
- **Headings**: text-dark-blue (#002142)
- **Body text**: neutral-800 (#171614)
- **Secondary text**: neutral-400
- **Borders**: outline (#DFDFDF) or neutral-100

