## Shared Components Library

Import from `@/components/formations-ui`:

### Layout
- `Header` — `variant: "desktop" | "mobile"`, `securedText?: string`
  - Formations + Forbes Advisor co-brand, lock icon, responsive
- `BackButton` — `onClick?: () => void`
  - ChevronLeft + "Back" text

### Buttons
- `CTAButton` — `variant: "primary" | "ghost"`, `fullWidth?: boolean`
  - Primary: bg-primary-500, white text, rounded-lg, h-14
  - Ghost: text-primary-500, underline, shadow-button
- `FormOption` — `label: string`, `selected?: boolean`, `onClick`
  - Radio-card pattern. Selected: border-primary-500. Default: border-outline

### Data Display
- `CheckItem` — `text: string` — green check circle + text row
- `CheckCircle` — standalone green check icon SVG
- `GreenBanner` — `text?: string` — green bg-secondary-500 uppercase bar
- `BonusCallout` — `regularText + highlightText` — green tint bg with discount icon
- `InfoBanner` — `icon?, text, learnMore?` — slate bg-info-bg with chevron
- `InfoTip` — `text: string` — bottom card tip with info icon
- `SocialProof` — `text + avatarSrcs?` — overlapping circles + trust text
- `Disclaimer` — `text: string` — centered small footnote text
- `PreferredPartnerBadge` — green pill badge

