## Component Patterns (for new components)

- **Buttons**: rounded-sm (8px), py-md px-lg, primary-500 bg, white text
- **Cards**: rounded-lg (16px), shadow-card, border border-outline, p-xl
- **Inputs**: rounded-sm, border-xs, p-sm, neutral-400 placeholder
- **Modals**: rounded-xl (24px), shadow-lg
- **Badges/Tags**: rounded-xs (4px), px-sm py-[2px]
- **Hover**: darken one stop (primary-500 → primary-600)
- **Disabled**: opacity-50
- **Focus rings**: 2px solid primary-400, 2px offset
- **Sticky footers**: shadow-sticky, border-t border-neutral-100
